      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Edmund Moshammer</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:177px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pub/edmund-moshammer/91/937/b21\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/6/66/EdmundMoshammer.jpg\" width=\"175\" height=\"175\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:EdmundMoshammer.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Edmund Moshammer <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Edmund Moshammer</b>,<br />\nan Austrian <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economics\">economist</a> currently at the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/European_Stability_Mechanism\">European Stability Mechanism</a>, holding a M.Sc. degree in specialized economic analysis from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barcelona_Graduate_School_of_Economics\">Barcelona Graduate School of Economics</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barcelona\">Barcelona</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catalonia\">Catalonia</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spain\">Spain</a> from 2014.\n</p><p>As avocational chess programmer Edmund Moshammer has been involved in the development of the <a href=\"/CPW-Engine\" title=\"CPW-Engine\">CPW-Engine</a> and <a href=\"/Glass\" title=\"Glass\">Glass Chess Engine</a>, working with <a href=\"/Pawel_Koziol\" title=\"Pawel Koziol\">Pawel Koziol</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. A side project was the creation of the Glass opening book format and the corresponding tool, the Glass Opening Book Manager <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. In March 2014, Edmund Moshammer introduced a port of <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> to <a href=\"/JavaScript\" title=\"JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> dubbed <a href=\"/index.php?title=JSUCI&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"JSUCI (page does not exist)\">JSUCI</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Fields_of_Interest\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Fields of Interest</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2009\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2009</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Fields_of_Interest\">Fields of Interest</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edmund_Moshammer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Fields of Interest\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><i>in Computerchess</i>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Corresponding_Squares\" title=\"Corresponding Squares\">Corresponding Squares</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Statistics</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edmund_Moshammer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/All_Shortest_Paths#Optimization\" title=\"All Shortest Paths\">All Shortest Paths - Optimization</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/CPW-Engine\" title=\"CPW-Engine\">CPW-Engine</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Glass\" title=\"Glass\">Glass</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=JSUCI&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"JSUCI (page does not exist)\">JSUCI</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edmund_Moshammer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2009\">2009</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edmund_Moshammer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2009\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26007\">EinStein würfelt nicht</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 14, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/EinStein_w%C3%BCrfelt_nicht!\" title=\"EinStein würfelt nicht!\">EinStein würfelt nicht!</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26783\">GUI in Visual Basic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 28, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a>, <a href=\"/Basic\" title=\"Basic\">Basic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26974\">PVS</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 12, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27516\">Elo Calcuation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 19, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Match Statistics</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27732\">Glass Opening Book Manager 1.0 - Released!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 03, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edmund_Moshammer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?start=0&amp;t=31699\">Engine Testing - Statistics</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 14, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Match Statistics</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34561\">DTS Structure</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 28, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Dynamic_Tree_Splitting\" title=\"Dynamic Tree Splitting\">Dynamic Tree Splitting</a>, <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a>, <a href=\"/Iterative_Search\" title=\"Iterative Search\">Iterative Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40931\">repetition detection</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 29, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42805\">New Database Storage Method</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 09, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">Databases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44347\">Compression of chess databases</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 09, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46828\">Ranking moves based on empirical information</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 10, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51763\">JSUCI 1.0 - connect javascript chess engines to UCI</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 28, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/JavaScript\" title=\"JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>, <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edmund_Moshammer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57149\">3D XPoint</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 02, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Memory\" title=\"Memory\">Memory</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59374\">Statistical assessment of chess opening book moves</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edmund_Moshammer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pub/edmund-moshammer/91/937/b21\">Edmund Moshammer | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.esm.europa.eu/research-staff/edmund-moshammer\">Edmund Moshammer | European Stability Mechanism</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pkoziol.cal24.pl/glass/\">Glass Homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sourceforge.net/projects/jsuci/\">Javascript Universal Chess Interface | Free software downloads at SourceForge.net</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/JavaScript\" title=\"JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>, <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edmund_Moshammer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pub/edmund-moshammer/91/937/b21\">Edmund Moshammer | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27731\">Glass 1.2 released</a> by <a href=\"/Pawel_Koziol\" title=\"Pawel Koziol\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 03, 2009</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27732\">Glass Opening Book Manager 1.0 - Released!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 03, 2009</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51763\">JSUCI 1.0 - connect javascript chess engines to UCI</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Edmund Moshammer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 28, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sourceforge.net/projects/jsuci/\">Javascript Universal Chess Interface | Free software downloads at SourceForge.net</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/3D_XPoint\">3D XPoint from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301154524\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.021 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.023 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 119/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 246/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with